snippet.title: Planet Fights - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
An online MMO game in which you can have your own virtual life. You can join a nation, buy vehicles, items, properties, open a political party, fight in battlefields, participate in races, take part in agent fights, be a nation senator or president, vote on nation issues and you can do many other activities.

Play the game on:
https://planetfights.com
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.SCLITIFYIT.PlanetFights
https://www.microsoft.com/store/apps/9MXFGV0WQ3RQ
